{"tid":328014,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改詞MV】《他約我去迪士尼後篇》（原曲：爭氣）","createTime":"2017-07-19T08:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T18:52:42.000Z","uid":48498,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f48449b0a3c936ae0df0ec7e68ecc8d6d0bc11","tid":328014,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"原曲：爭氣<br />\n主唱：走地貓<br />\n改詞：大豬包包<br />\n混音：雪人也出火<br />\n影片製作：大豬包包<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n城堡 被濃霧蠶食般 入侵了 這美麗<br />\n塵封的 那木馬 未放聲 像往日 在兜圈<br />\n大象先生 你會否於天空 像起舞般暢遊<br />\n唱著離謌 今天唯獨我 在探戈<br />\n<br />\n伴我玩到倦了 在咖啡杯上炫耀<br />\n共挽手與高飛狗親吻 快樂在映照<br />\n騎木馬 仍尖叫 你卻偷 偷在笑<br />\n為何 呆望這門票 哭了<br />\n沒有公主 那命數 伴我悲傷在流露<br />\n剩廢墟般的公園跟我 徹夜在哭訴<br />\n無辦法修補 童話破碎 無預告<br />\n故事 到此刻鐘全儘耗<br />\n<br />\n坐著魔氈 勉強也飛不到沒魔法<br />\n難自救 這荒廢的樂園 遺留下我 在顫抖<br />\n<br />\n沒阿拉丁去共舞 坐那飛氈在迷霧<br />\n沒你於身邊穿梭堡壘 美夢在消耗<br />\n無白雪 來傾訴  在痛悲 不用抱<br />\n為何沉睡那幻影宣告<br />\n<br />\n城堡 根本不會改變 是我幻覺的變遷<br />\n米老鼠 照舊在精品店 人人在笑 我怎麼哭了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幻覺終於領悟了 是我悲傷在炫耀<br />\n令我的 痛苦傷心黑暗霸著在映照<br />\n園內聽 人歡笑 我的心 不願笑<br />\n現時 呆望這門票 哭了<br />\n望那煙火快儘耗 伴我悲傷在流露<br />\n在對比 這公園的歡笑快樂夢指數<br />\n無辦法修補 童話破碎 無預告<br />\n得我 看到荒土 來獨舞<br />\n<br />\nYoutube :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLR2B3BYwLU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMLR2B3BYwLU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=20gSK6ztPuvmwsvB4reee%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d052e544\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLR2B3BYwLU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"d641564fa3721eb4b52104c522b65b3c0dc64ebf","tid":328014,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"雪人也出火<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HornySnowman/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHornySnowman%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=20gSK6ztPuvmwsvB4reee%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=aded030a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HornySnowman/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n走地貓Channel :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-Ct5fZ0F47qNG3biWAZKFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC-Ct5fZ0F47qNG3biWAZKFA&d=20gSK6ztPuvmwsvB4reee%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a24af0c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-Ct5fZ0F47qNG3biWAZKFA</a><br />\n<br />\n大豬包包<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BigPiggyBreadBread/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBigPiggyBreadBread%2F&d=20gSK6ztPuvmwsvB4reee%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=77564616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BigPiggyBreadBread/</a>"},{"pid":"199935d903836ac3d0f6eae05d1bd0af14c66ebc","tid":328014,"uid":48498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"十年前，香港迪士尼開幕，《他約我去迪士尼》相信大家都聽過，以前聽嘅時候總係覺得字裏行間帶有一絲一毫嘅傷感，好似去完就唔會再有牽連咁。所以就諗如果男女主角自己再去嘅時候嘅迪士尼會係一個點樣嘅迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba24532ec658cd67cf364ee75f296ca4b0ba09b2","tid":328014,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"多謝雪巴嘅混音同走地貓肯唱小弟嘅劣作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n任屌唔嬲，俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者分享下迪士尼嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dc7a5d80e8169683f0fbb11dd707461f7f0b5b","tid":328014,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"舊post :<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248219/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248219/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"2b1f29934f86703512ab10da2ad4d93bf86476ac","tid":328014,"uid":484